    "body": "If the goal is to just figure why the compiler made the decisions it did, another option would be to add some nicer `info!` statements explaining exactly what happened. It wouldn't give you a compile-time guarantee that you have a static or dynamic product, but it would avoid adding more codegen flags.\n",
