    "body": "That would be a helpful stop-gap, but I don't think `RUST_LOG=rustc::...=info rustc lib.rs` is a very nice long term solution.\n\nMaybe we replace `prefer-dynamic` with `linkage=...` which would allow `static`, `dynamic`, `prefer-static` (default) and `prefer-dynamic`. (Or even just `static`, `dynamic` with `auto` for the autoselected default, no need for the `prefer-...` options.)\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
